news.title: Nainital HC issues bailable warrant against MDDA secretary
news.para: Warrant was issued for not filing a reply to the court's earlier order on a PIL filed against alleged construction of illegal colonies on land earmarked for parks in Banjarawala and Ajabpur Kala areas of Dehradun.

news.title: RERA practices are far better in Nashik: Vasant Prabhu, Secretary, MahaRERA
news.para: Prabhu said the complaints regarding real estate projects registered under RERA in Nashik region are lesser, and compliance is also good.

news.title: Bharat Housing Network raises Rs 125 crore in series-A funding round
news.para: Varanium NexGen Fund, 9Unicorns, Riverwalk Holdings, SMK Ventures, DMI Sparkle Fund, LC Nueva and other investors have also participated in series-A funding round of Bharat Housing Network.

news.title: NDTV leases 1.28 lakh sq ft at Max Square in Noida
news.para: Max Square will also house Skootr, which has leased approximately 103,000 sq ft of super built up area. Total leasable area for the project is about 0.7 million sq ft. New York Life Insurance Company is a 49% partner in the project.

news.title: To avail benefits of registration extension, promoters must upload QPR on portal: UP-RERA
news.para: Promoters of 732 projects have not filled targets and promoters of 356 projects have not updated targets on the portal. Hence, UP-RERA has imposed penalty of Rs 2 lakh per project on 732 projects and Rs 1 lakh per project on 356 projects.

news.title: Sebi to auction 13 properties of Bishal Group of companies, NVD Solar on Dec 12
news.para: Of the 13 properties, eight are related to Bishal Group of companies (Bishal Abasan India Ltd, Bishal Distillers Ltd, Bishal Agri-Bio Industries Ltd, Bishal Horticulture and Animal Projects Ltd) and five belong to NVD Solar.

news.title: Snaptrude raises $14 million led by Foundamental VC, Accel
news.para: The latest capital infusion will help Snaptrude's efforts to expand its product and engineering teams and its go-to-market strategy, enabling it to reach more architecture firms.

news.title: South Delhi's only 100-meter skyscraper receives OC
news.para: Located in Singapore, Risland has a presence in over 9 countries and regions across the globe with a total residential portfolio of 1 lakh crores and 40,000+ happy families.

news.title: Star Housing Finance raises Rs 60 crore capital for expansion
news.para: Star Housing Finance's assets under management (AUM) as of September 30, 2023, increased 110% year-on-year to Rs 319.43 crore. The company disbursed Rs 108.30 crore during H1 FY24, registering a year-on-year growth of 49%.

news.title: Signatureglobal (India) posts net loss of Rs 19.92 crore in Q2 FY24
news.para: Signatureglobal (India)'s net consolidated total income stood at Rs 121.16 crore in Q2 FY24, a dip of 10.70 per cent from Rs 135.68 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Omaxe posts net loss of Rs 84.35 crore in Q2 FY24
news.para: Omaxe's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 269.82 crore in Q2 FY24, a growth of 120.66 per cent from Rs 122.28 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Piramal Enterprises posts net profit of Rs 48.19 crore in Q2 FY24
news.para: Piramal Enterprises' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 2,205.21 crore in Q2 FY24, a growth of 12.73 per cent from Rs 1,956.23 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: The Ramco Cements posts net profit of Rs 72 crore in Q2 FY24
news.para: The Ramco Cements' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 2,352.09 crore in Q2 FY24, a growth of 30.63 per cent from Rs 1,800.61 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Delhi HC quashes DDA demolition notice for encroachment removal in Mehrauli
news.para: A bench headed by Chief Justice Satish Chandra Sharma said regardless of the environmental imperatives or earlier court orders, the DDA's obligation to act as per law and ensure procedural fairness to those affected by its actions remains intact.

news.title: NBCC (India)'s net profit declines 16.19% in Q2 FY24
news.para: NBCC (India)'s net consolidated total income stood at Rs 2,129.09 crore in Q2 FY24, a growth of 2.66 per cent from Rs 2,073.89 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Orient Cement posts net profit of Rs 24.62 crore in Q2 FY24
news.para: Orient Cement's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 722.24 crore in Q2 FY24, a growth of 16.47 per cent from Rs 620.11 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Coimbatore corporation to resume installation of streetlights
news.para: During the recent council meeting, city mayor Kalpana Anand Kumar had assured that there would not be any compromise on the quality of the lights.

news.title: Canara Bank raises lending rate by 5 basis points across tenure
news.para: The revised marginal cost of funds-based lending rate (MCLR) across various tenors would be effective from November 12, Canara Bank said in a regulatory filing.

news.title: Shalimar Paints' net loss widens to Rs 25.62 crore in Q2 FY24
news.para: Shalimar Paints' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 121.41 crore in Q2 FY24, a growth of 8.57 per cent from Rs 111.83 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Pimpri Chinchwad: PCMC gets cracking on dust pollution, to hold officials accountable for lapses
news.para: While a majority of these guidelines already exist, PCMC now aims at enforcing them strictly, for which dedicated squads have been deployed in each ward to ensure compliance.
